divs: sighting detailsnumerous emails have been sent to the webmaster at mufon asking why the link to access the latest 20 ufo sightings is not working and so far it is still directing us to fill out a sighting form. so many people rely on this website for current information as a tool to track et\ufo sightings and the fact that this issue has still not been addressed is disturbing to say the least. i hope that mufon is still a viable source of information going forward in the future. to lose this valuable website would be a terrible loss indeed. please post something on the main webpage to let us know what is going on please !
Summary: Why is the link for the last 20 UFO sightings still broken?
